    "en": {
      "title": "40 lakh people register for the National Fuel Licence",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "40 lakh people were registered for National Fuel License as of last night (26) and at 299 Cipetco filling stations and I.O.C. 92,845 kw.r. of people at 34 filling stations. Electricity and Energy Minister Kanchana Wijesekera said that the system had been used.",
        "The Minister further mentions that 2,364,434 motorcycles and 723,022 tricycles have been registered with the National Fuel License as of last night."
      ],
